---
title: Homestyle Satay Beef & Veggie Curry with Rapid Rice
description: A satay beef curry, it has our hearts fluttering and our mouths watering as the hearty curry aromas sweep the kitchen. On a bed of fluffy rice, we’re head over heels for this curry!

